#PMGHowTo
— Blend a wash of ‘BRONZE DEVOTION’ eye shadow through the outer corner, crease & along the lower lash line
— Use ‘ROSEWOOD ROMANTIQUE’ eye shadow to shade the inner & outer corner with a blending brush
— Apply ‘ROSEWOOD ROMANTIQUE’ eye shadow along the lower lash line
— Add depth to the outer half of the lash line with ‘XTREME NOCTURNE’ eye shadow & blend outwards
— Use a small detail brush to apply ‘XTREME NOCTURNE’ eye shadow along the outer half of the lower lash line
— Add definition along the lash line with ‘XTREME NOCTURNE’ eye shadow
— Swipe ‘BLITZ VENUS’ pigment across the lid with a dampened brush
— Blend ‘ROSEWOOD ROMANTIQUE’ eye shadow through the crease
— Line the lash line with Perma Precision Liquid Eyeliner & extend into a wing
— Apply FetishEYES Mascara & false lashes
— Highlight the brow bone with ‘SKINTENSE GLOW’ eye shadow
